data.description: Great opportunity!  Rehabbed Large Greystone ready for your cosmetic touch-ups located on a tree lined street in the Greater Grand Crossing neighborhood of Chicago. Many nice features including original hardwood floors, 3 bedrooms in each unit, 2 baths in one and 1 1/2 baths in another unit, washer/dryer hook-up in each unit, bay windows in living rooms, full basement that can be duplexed, new central air/heating, and a 2-car detached garage. The 2nd floor unit has a formal dining room. Sold as-is.
